flowchart TD
    %% Brownfield Flow — archaeology before bootstrap, research before requirements

    CODE[(Existing Codebase<br/>code + tests + history)] --> BOOT["install.sh<br/>Seed skills, rules, and memories"]:::brown
    BOOT --> INIT["starter-init (Phase A + B)<br/>Phase A: Archaeology subagent sweep & map debt<br/>Phase B: Bootstrap config & seed memories"]:::brown

    INIT --> SESSION_START["context-session START<br/>Load context & claim feature"]:::step
    SESSION_START --> RES["spec-research<br/>(analysis.md: map boundaries & behaviors to preserve)"]:::brown

    RES --> SPEC["spec-requirements<br/>(grilling waves + spec.md with brownfield risk rating)"]:::brown
    SPEC --> PLAN["spec-plan<br/>(plan.md + tasks.md)"]:::brown
    PLAN --> IMPL["spec-implement<br/>(one task at a time + proof)"]:::step
    IMPL --> VERIFY["harness-verify<br/>(review.md + testing-scenarios.md + optional Fallow Pass)"]:::gate

    VERIFY -- gate fail --> IMPL
    VERIFY -- pass --> SYNC["Post-Ship Sync<br/>(context-memory sweep)"]:::gate
    SYNC --> ENDS["context-session END<br/>(handoff.md + session-extracts.md)"]:::step
    ENDS --> DONE([Feature Shipped + KB compounded]):::terminal

    classDef terminal fill:#0d0d0d,stroke:#0d0d0d,color:#fff
    classDef brown fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#b45309,color:#fff
    classDef step fill:#fff,stroke:#d0d7de,color:#0d0d0d
    classDef gate fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1d4ed8,color:#fff

    class CODE,DONE terminal
